{"tid":387254,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人游自由式好快冇氣?","createTime":"2017-09-04T13:14:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T13:24:57.000Z","uid":132653,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"322450bc96fbdc2f67d5c030df0268858398d042","tid":387254,"uid":132653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:14:12.000Z","msg":"蛙式學緊自由式 , 我蛙式快游1k都冇問題, 但一游自由式就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自學左幾星期,動作 踢水應該都冇咩問題,個人唔會沉 但次次游到一半都冇曬氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最盡淨係游到一個池(25m)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   不過都算進步左,原本一半都冇氣<br />\n<br />\n想問下游自由式係唔係要慢慢習慣個換氣方式?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236a4ab0d4b2ded32abbd9e19923ffcd328b16fd","tid":387254,"uid":135178,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:17:49.000Z","msg":"每一下手sin耐啲 兩下手一啖氣 再慢慢加上去 希望幫到你"},{"pid":"64d4f9275ac537e816302125d1365e3f51d7ade3","tid":387254,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:18:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蛙式學緊自由式 , 我蛙式快游1k都冇問題, 但一游自由式就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自學左幾星期,動作 踢水應該都冇咩問題,個人唔會沉 但次次游到一半都冇曬氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最盡淨係游到一個池(25m)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   不過都算進步左,原本一半都冇氣<br />\n<br />\n想問下游自由式係唔係要慢慢習慣個換氣方式?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺得自由式好晒力，但D人又可以一支箭係咁去。利申：游唔到50米，蛙式卻冇問題"},{"pid":"0a675d09fa8ce8ef08a170d28d7d01f8584810dc","tid":387254,"uid":135178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:19:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每一下手sin耐啲 兩下手一啖氣 再慢慢加上去 希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n同埋條腰要左右轉 配合隻手 伸到盡 運用哂每一下嘅速度 會慳力好多"},{"pid":"9a1c1ca3a24e007658585b62f5da202b00e4aea9","tid":387254,"uid":132653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:19:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每一下手sin耐啲 兩下手一啖氣 再慢慢加上去 希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會多d練 聽日試下sin耐d"},{"pid":"2b1103826af6d439dd13ffbfad5e70fd2193af4b","tid":387254,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"努力練習 用毅力克服所有難關"},{"pid":"de9f72fc98ffe00d43a50de9029db4408d35f4eb","tid":387254,"uid":132653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:20:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>每一下手sin耐啲 兩下手一啖氣 再慢慢加上去 希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n同埋條腰要左右轉 配合隻手 伸到盡 運用哂每一下嘅速度 會慳力好多</blockquote><br />\n我有左右轉, 但次次換氣出問題 , 可能係習慣左蛙式果個換氣 (比較長)<br />\n<br />\n自由式要慢慢練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21ae5417359a75f8389be90df7d3806e6dcbbc9e","tid":387254,"uid":132653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:21:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蛙式學緊自由式 , 我蛙式快游1k都冇問題, 但一游自由式就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自學左幾星期,動作 踢水應該都冇咩問題,個人唔會沉 但次次游到一半都冇曬氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最盡淨係游到一個池(25m)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   不過都算進步左,原本一半都冇氣<br />\n<br />\n想問下游自由式係唔係要慢慢習慣個換氣方式?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺得自由式好晒力，但D人又可以一支箭係咁去。利申：游唔到50米，蛙式卻冇問題</blockquote><br />\n我都係,可能蛙式太易換氣,又唔駛係水太耐,所以我地一游自由式就出事,要慢慢練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fabb3505e7d8a390c553bf35f705fdafe1869b66","tid":387254,"uid":135178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:22:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每一下手sin耐啲 兩下手一啖氣 再慢慢加上去 希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n同埋條腰要左右轉 配合隻手 伸到盡 運用哂每一下嘅速度 會慳力好多</blockquote><br />\n我有左右轉, 但次次換氣出問題 , 可能係習慣左蛙式果個換氣 (比較長)<br />\n<br />\n自由式要慢慢練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會係你抖氣個陣用條腰發力 或者姿勢時間唔啱 令到個人好阻水? btw自學真係犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b360300941bcd5ad6e7b19f474b15cd7e1e17aa","tid":387254,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"蛙仔游唔掂<br />\n自由式好舒服"},{"pid":"00f2220d76fcb8637cad1b7231e8461f6de5d275","tid":387254,"uid":132653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每一下手sin耐啲 兩下手一啖氣 再慢慢加上去 希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n同埋條腰要左右轉 配合隻手 伸到盡 運用哂每一下嘅速度 會慳力好多</blockquote><br />\n我有左右轉, 但次次換氣出問題 , 可能係習慣左蛙式果個換氣 (比較長)<br />\n<br />\n自由式要慢慢練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會唔會係你抖氣個陣用條腰發力</span> 或者姿勢時間唔啱 令到個人好阻水? btw自學真係犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又好似真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正常係腰轉完 得返頭用力?<br />\n<br />\nbtw 我蛙式初初都自學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  果陣水深d都唔敢行去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2b3cc59460d82465355f1eac2795b0297f70d6","tid":387254,"uid":135178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T13:28:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>每一下手sin耐啲 兩下手一啖氣 再慢慢加上去 希望幫到你</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n同埋條腰要左右轉 配合隻手 伸到盡 運用哂每一下嘅速度 會慳力好多</blockquote><br />\n我有左右轉, 但次次換氣出問題 , 可能係習慣左蛙式果個換氣 (比較長)<br />\n<br />\n自由式要慢慢練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會唔會係你抖氣個陣用條腰發力</span> 或者姿勢時間唔啱 令到個人好阻水? btw自學真係犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又好似真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /