n身輕微咁轉 主要係頭轉 個頭啱啱高過水面就夠 或者你試下專練向右抖氣先 記住要保持個身係伸直 令自己唔好阻水 保持速度</blockquote><br />\n你同個初學講經咩 個頭貼水面換氣 飲水都飲飽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有咁高拎咁高 最緊要夠時間換氣<br />\n試下游左手返返去前面 先游右手 等手自由式  攞岩個節奏先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你廢緊係飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 樓主岩岩自學 你當佢好叻咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩識游唔夠氣 貼水面邊夠時間換氣啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n依家係唔夠氣 唔係抖唔到氣 你仲叫佢有咁高抬咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔識游就唔好出聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8da7c45769905c8ffc764d924beb057d7f0256","tid":387254,"uid":40461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T14:37:21.000Z","msg":"我同樓主一樣，游頭幾下都可以，游到30M左右就開始索氣"},{"pid":"b91332936d20bd844fceb845d237372cda807d5a","tid":387254,"uid":41542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:05:14.000Z","msg":"樓主你都係初學姐 岩岩學比較喘氣係正常嘅 上面有人提議等手自由式都係個唔錯嘅練習<br />\n不過自由划手抖氣時需要有d水感 同踢腳唔沉唔同 係兩回事<br />\n<br />\n（樓主唔好介意 我見游泳d人踢腳都唔係好岩 你覺得跟足片練習 水底動作往往係另一回事 以前我淨係執動作都比教練執左好幾年）<br />\n<br />\n利申以前練水教水"},{"pid":"6d0921d811cac42c0b7c51f91b409cad7dc3ac2a","tid":387254,"uid":41542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:05:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你都係初學姐 岩岩學比較喘氣係正常嘅 上面有人提議等手自由式都係個唔錯嘅練習<br />\n不過自由划手抖氣時需要有d水感 同踢腳唔沉唔同 係兩回事<br />\n<br />\n（樓主唔好介意 我見<span style=\"color: red;\">泳池</span>d人踢腳都唔係好岩 你覺得跟足片練習 水底動作往往係另一回事 以前我淨係執動作都比教練執左好幾年）<br />\n<br />\n利申以前練水教水</blockquote>"},{"pid":"05c2539c6ab32874a8696cf96927813a4942b299","tid":387254,"uid":105462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:12:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主你都係初學姐 岩岩學比較喘氣係正常嘅 上面有人提議等手自由式都係個唔錯嘅練習<br />\n不過自由划手抖氣時需要有d水感 同踢腳唔沉唔同 係兩回事<br />\n<br />\n（樓主唔好介意 我見<span style=\"color: red;\">泳池</span>d人踢腳都唔係好岩 你覺得跟足片練習 水底動作往往係另一回事 以前我淨係執動作都比教練執左好幾年）<br />\n<br />\n利申以前練水教水</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n游泳池10個都唔知有無1個係標準動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢都係想自學下姐 <br />\n<br />\n我記得好似係可以捉住池邊踢腳練換氣 <br />\n習慣個動作<br />\n另外游既時候記得睇前面  係游泳池見到好多人游自由式唔睇前面 2邊攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56ad59b0823ef279d618fed7d68ae5229eb4b80","tid":387254,"uid":99602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:33:08.000Z","msg":"其實自由式踢水要幾快先啱？ 手定腳重要啲？"},{"pid":"a18db37371916a8a289e4eed867525e85899f37a","tid":387254,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"試下學破冰轉身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e1f4edff520a2ab30469d90f32ac184c55e7cc","tid":387254,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T15:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實自由式踢水要幾快先啱？ 手定腳重要啲？</blockquote><br />\n有幾快踢幾快"},{"pid":"eaa1fbe1fcc0a04e6ad99369840aabc9470b166f","tid":387254,"uid":99602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:12:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實自由式踢水要幾快先啱？ 手定腳重要啲？</blockquote><br />\n有幾快踢幾快</blockquote><br />\n唔知點解我踢極個下身都係沉嘅，同埋踢得快，游幾步已經無氣，焗住游番蛙式<br />\n<br />\n另外，其實踢水係要大脾同小腿都登直哂去踢，還是唔駛刻意理佢，膝頭曲都ok?"},{"pid":"5a0a17fdf4adba68bbd9740bfa05381e12a69e45","tid":387254,"uid":142532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:17:44.000Z","msg":"我反而係夠氣但唔夠力"},{"pid":"88e80d4f19b956cff7e960d6edca27d812c54c3d","tid":387254,"uid":133588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:22:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而係夠氣但唔夠力</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下放鬆d，有時係緊張所以肌肉緊左用多左力。<br />\n<br />\n（泳隊+教水+救生員）"},{"pid":"55a0309a791b01aead482e4dd8ed26032c0f5b95","tid":387254,"uid":133588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實自由式踢水要幾快先啱？ 手定腳重要啲？</blockquote><br />\n有幾快踢幾快</blockquote><br />\n唔知點解我踢極個下身都係沉嘅，同埋踢得快，游幾步已經無氣，焗住游番蛙式<br />\n<br />\n另外，其實踢水係要大脾同小腿都登直哂去踢，還是唔駛刻意理佢，膝頭曲都ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實條腰都要用力去 keep住直。<br />\n腳沉係你個頭太高，試下將壓心口落水，對腳會浮返上來。"},{"pid":"1df258040b0d26165beeb578be1288ad180282e6","tid":387254,"uid":98413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:42:35.000Z","msg":"我游50米已經冇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：蛙式可以一口氣游3k"},{"pid":"11956596f3922f4a34153c1f3608d82caad9ffd4","tid":387254,"uid":74933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:50:36.000Z","msg":"由細學自由式先 衝完會索氣但好爽<br />\n學蛙式 蛙黎蛙去都前進唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a02d56c0c1f00254da2300176842504f1f255c0f","tid":387254,"uid":52182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我游50米已經冇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：蛙式可以一口氣游3k</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一口氣游3k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f88830d84ea2045b26cbb0b50ff045b69a53c429","tid":387254,"uid":9142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T16:53:57.000Z","msg":"有冇諗過其實係冇呼氣？我當你頭幾淡吸得夠氣，但如果一直都冇呼返出黎，之後吸幾多都冇用。你依家試下就咁吸多過呼，都應該會慢慢開始唔夠氣，莫講話係水度。"},{"pid":"2a71b109921b00edb410709a2204f171657a436a","tid":387254,"uid":64607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T18:43:30.000Z","msg":"lm <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3471eb9a15762daea61ca69dbc890f1493b2b9ec","tid":387254,"uid":106614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:18:49.000Z","msg":"游自由式一吸氣就飲水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a7908faecd6eb3c20724380f6d90b451dcf5b6","tid":387254,"uid":96707,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T19:19:31.000Z","msg":"自由式要訣係當隻手喺水裏面時要lock住成隻手嘅pose<br />\n唔好用手臂力<br />\n要用肩背力黎帶動隻手黎游<br />\n咁樣就會無咁快攰<br />\n同樣對腳踢水時淨係用大腿力<br />\n放鬆小腿<br />\n踢水幅度要大<br />\n利申：以前做過救生，自由式1000m當熱身"},{"pid":"815d8809807da3139bab4267636c71eebb9114f3","tid":387254,"uid":133588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T21:38:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">自由式要訣係當隻手喺水裏面時要lock住成隻手嘅pose</span><br />\n唔好用手臂力<br />\n要用肩背力黎帶動隻手黎游<br />\n咁樣就會無咁快攰<br />\n同樣對腳踢水時淨係用大腿力<br />\n放鬆小腿<br />\n踢水幅度要大<br />\n利申：以前做過救生，自由式1000m當熱身</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解唔係細細開始學游水的人好多都係講緊都get唔到呢點。有時教朋友游教到好無力。"},{"pid":"3799082180fcdd2175cbf4fd36fdd3dcd2f77cec","tid":387254,"uid":76523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T21:57:16.000Z","msg":"自學可能會比較難～因為姿勢方面未必做得好，無人指點到你<br />\n<br />\n例如對手要貼大脾去到最盡<br />\n向前fing上去要用肩頭力放到盡<br />\n唔好用死力同貼耳仔<br />\n<br />\n你動作唔岩用死力就會好累，自然條氣會唔順搞到咁<br />\n小弟最近考完磁章有唔少師兄吹開水都有講依個問題<br />\n我諗一黎係動作問題，二黎可以試下自由式慢慢游100米 100米咁捱下池 習慣就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc862dfc97d74d6708981291b7bb71a359ceb52","tid":387254,"uid":91798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T22:55:07.000Z","msg":"樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都自學 最近游到42秒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過來人話你知<br />\n如果游緊果陣盡量壓個頭同個胸<br />\n直到你覺得屎忽貼水面 踢腳有水花<br />\n就會快好多<br />\n仲有踢腳唔好用盡奶力咁去踢住先<br />\n會用好多氣同好多力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都想進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搭單問有冇人講解下high elbow catch, rotation同推水既發力同timing應該係點？"},{"pid":"5d5ca056de6210d590399a1474ec5621f68f0069","tid":387254,"uid":133588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T22:59:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都自學 最近游到42秒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過來人話你知<br />\n如果游緊果陣盡量壓個頭同個胸<br />\n直到你覺得屎忽貼水面 踢腳有水花<br />\n就會快好多<br />\n仲有踢腳唔好用盡奶力咁去踢住先<br />\n會用好多氣同好多力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都想進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搭單問有冇人講解下high elbow catch, rotation同推水既發力同timing應該係點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhigh elbow catch<br />\n只郁前臂，shoulder lock住。<br />\n拉到鼻前先好郁elbow以上的部分。<br />\n呢個時候同時"},{"pid":"0af78c1816943f68de24bf10f4d765930da53b09","tid":387254,"uid":133588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T23:02:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都自學 最近游到42秒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過來人話你知<br />\n如果游緊果陣盡量壓個頭同個胸<br />\n直到你覺得屎忽貼水面 踢腳有水花<br />\n就會快好多<br />\n仲有踢腳唔好用盡奶力咁去踢住先<br />\n會用好多氣同好多力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都想進步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搭單問有冇人講解下high elbow catch, rotation同推水既發力同timing應該係點？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nhigh elbow catch<br />\n只郁前臂，shoulder lock住。<br />\n拉到鼻前先好郁elbow以上的部分。<br />\n呢個時候同時</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同時配合rotation。shoulder以下轉。<br />\n用rotation帶動一口氣推到手掌掂大腿。<br />\n<br />\n練的時候最好將一個個動作斬件練。<br />\n<br />\n用文字教水好難啊！！！"}]}